title: War Of The Roses: He gets notifications I haven't heard before
description: Trent called in for War Of The Roses today and is concerned about some of the things he's seeing / hearing with his boyfriend, Alex. Something to do with a notification he hears from Alex's phone every night & things showing up in the house that Trent KNOWS Alex wouldn't go out and buy.
